column5: Quite an accomplishment, definitely a challenge to catch the absolute smallest fish in the world!
I think i got her beat. Caught a 6 inch walleye tonite Im sure the pic will be up soon enough
If you were taking pictures who poured water over the reel to keep the gears from burning up? LOL
A smart man would have told her that was 8 inches  .  All kidding aside hopefully she is bitten by the fishing bug.  My wife loves to fish which is great.   Ian
I am not sure I have ever seen a 20ft tall woman. Nice fish.   Art
Nice catch........and the fish ain't that bad!
Very cool its nice to see such a great smile for that monster she just might be a keeper
